---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Agencia de Marketing y Sistemas">
	<section class="relative bg-quinet-dark text-quinet-white overflow-hidden min-h-[90vh] flex items-center">
		
		<div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full overflow-hidden -z-10 pointer-events-none">
			<div class="absolute top-[-20%] left-[-10%] w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-quinet-teal/20 blur-[120px]"></div>
			<div class="absolute bottom-[-20%] right-[-10%] w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-quinet-gold/10 blur-[100px]"></div>
		</div>

		<div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 py-25 lg:py-32 text-center relative z-10">
			
			<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm mb-8 animate-fade-in-up shadow-sm">
				<span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
				  <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-quinet-gold opacity-75"></span>
				  <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-quinet-gold"></span>
				</span>
				<span class="text-sm font-medium text-quinet-white/90">Especialistas en Escalar Negocios 🚀</span>
			</div>

			<h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight">
				Tu negocio no necesita seguidores, <br class="hidden md:block" />
				<span class="text-transparent uppercase bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-quinet-teal to-quinet-gold">
					necesita un sistema de ventas.
				</span>
			</h1>

			<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-quinet-white/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 font-sans leading-relaxed">
				¿Cansado de perder oportunidades de venta? Implementamos embudos automatizados y tecnología para que tu negocio facture 24/7.
			</p>

			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
				<a href="https://wa.me/+543812529020" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-quinet-gold hover:bg-white text-quinet-dark font-bold rounded-full transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(233,196,106,0.3)]">
					Agendar Auditoría Gratis 🎯
				</a>
				<a href="#servicios" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 text-quinet-white border border-white/10 font-semibold rounded-full transition-all duration-300 backdrop-blur-sm">
					Ver nuestros ecosistemas 👇
				</a>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
				<p class="text-sm text-quinet-white/50 mb-4 font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Potenciando marcas con tecnología de punta</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="servicios" class="bg-quinet-light text-quinet-dark py-24 relative">
		<div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4">
			
			<div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
				<span class="text-quinet-teal font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm mb-3 block">El Ecosistema Quinet</span>
				<h2 class="font-display uppercase text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6">
					Construimos tu máquina de <span class="text-quinet-gold">generar clientes.</span>
				</h2>
				<p class="text-quinet-dark/70 text-lg font-sans">
					No ofrecemos "posteos lindos". Implementamos sistemas integrales donde cada pieza tiene un único objetivo: aumentar la facturación de tu negocio.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
				
				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-black/5 group">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-quinet-light rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
						💻
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold mb-3">Páginas Web</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-quinet-dark/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
						Diseñamos tu sucursal digital. Webs ultra rápidas y optimizadas para que tu negocio transmita máxima autoridad.
					</p>
					<a href="/servicios/paginas-web" class="inline-flex items-center text-quinet-teal font-bold hover:text-quinet-dark transition-colors">
						Saber más <span class="ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">→</span>
					</a>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-black/5 group">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-quinet-light rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
						🌪️
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold mb-3">Funnels de Venta</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-quinet-dark/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
						Sistemas automatizados (Landing + Emails) que filtran curiosos y te entregan clientes listos para comprar.
					</p>
					<a href="/servicios/embudos-de-venta" class="inline-flex items-center text-quinet-teal font-bold hover:text-quinet-dark transition-colors">
						Saber más <span class="ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">→</span>
					</a>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-black/5 group">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-quinet-light rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
						🎯
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold mb-3">Meta Ads</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-quinet-dark/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
						Compramos la atención de tu cliente ideal en Instagram y Facebook para inyectar tráfico directo a tu negocio.
					</p>
					<a href="/servicios/meta-ads" class="inline-flex items-center text-quinet-teal font-bold hover:text-quinet-dark transition-colors">
						Saber más <span class="ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">→</span>
					</a>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-black/5 group">
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-quinet-light rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
						📱
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold mb-3">Gestión de Redes</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-quinet-dark/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
						Contenido estratégico y diseño premium para que tu marca destaque visualmente y construya una comunidad fiel.
					</p>
					<a href="/servicios/community-manager" class="inline-flex items-center text-quinet-teal font-bold hover:text-quinet-dark transition-colors">
						Saber más <span class="ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">→</span>
					</a>
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="bg-quinet-light pb-24 px-4">
		<div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
			<div class="bg-quinet-dark rounded-[3rem] p-10 md:p-20 text-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-white/5">
				
				<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30 pointer-events-none">
					<div class="absolute -top-32 -right-32 w-96 h-96 bg-quinet-teal rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
					<div class="absolute -bottom-32 -left-32 w-96 h-96 bg-quinet-gold rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
				</div>

				<div class="relative z-10">
					<span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-quinet-teal/20 text-quinet-teal text-sm font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-8 border border-quinet-teal/30">
						<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-quinet-teal animate-pulse"></span>
						Cupos Limitados
					</span>
					
					<h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-quinet-white mb-6 leading-tight">
						¿Listo para escalar <br class="hidden md:block"/> tu negocio?
					</h2>
					<p class="text-quinet-white/70 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 font-sans">
						Dejá de perder tiempo con estrategias que no convierten. Escribinos hoy y diseñemos el ecosistema digital que te va a traer ventas en automático.
					</p>
					
					<div class="flex justify-center">
						<a href="https://wa.me/+543812529020" class="group relative px-8 py-5 bg-quinet-gold hover:bg-white text-quinet-dark font-extrabold rounded-full transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(233,196,106,0.2)] hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(233,196,106,0.5)] flex items-center gap-3 text-lg">
							<span>Hablemos por WhatsApp</span>
							<span class="text-2xl group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-300">💬</span>
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	</Layout>